{"tid":2490354,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"在港日本電影迷：自從戲院被強制收皮之後，好多電影係香港都冇份睇。","createTime":"2021-04-15T13:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T16:39:46.000Z","uid":158885,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b4d3cc4e86c02432a18ae1ccb6865302ec3a28","tid":2490354,"uid":158885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"我就係標題個電影迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排追劇鐘意左睇吉高由理子做啲戲，先發現佢有套《想見你的愛》係今年年頭上映。<br />\n不過香港戲院就冇份，依家上網搵線上看都冇。<br />\n一個肺炎就收哂電影業皮。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚，有冇巴絲原來好期待嘅戲，去到依家都冇機會睇。"},{"pid":"32d5beadb3f374b54ddeee4e2dc27412ba86dae5","tid":2490354,"uid":159266,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"未必關事, 就算冇肺炎, 香港都唔係套套外語片都會上"},{"pid":"5eef9e137ef41829c2fc5fd193708321c280e7d0","tid":2490354,"uid":89608,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:54:28.000Z","msg":"樓主以為全世界既戲都會係香港戲院上......"},{"pid":"44d8c35f58def0305796be13ba29d1b95bcddab9","tid":2490354,"uid":71259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔係套套都會上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58db7f50cf95cc3f50e8b4ed3c7d436b81a45c9","tid":2490354,"uid":92700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"日本戲唔係大路野都幾難會上"},{"pid":"77db8e79ca3edd06000cff4c91b3aa4ba27078b6","tid":2490354,"uid":236359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"你又係日本電影迷？我又係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39577fa015764fab8af33bdf6be0771aeacf249a","tid":2490354,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"慣哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea722102c0797c6b35b373808da39ec3079da3d8","tid":2490354,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r